data.value:
After that click the play button to start: > Searching for the ISBN > Get data from amazon > Generate eBook.zip format
- This is a multithreaded application when a thread finds a ISBN and gets data from amazon you will see a green flag - If he couldn't find the ISBN you will see a red flag - If he found an ISBN string but can't extract the ISBN number you will see an gray flag and be able to manually extract it. - If he couldn' find the information on amazon you will see a yellow flag
- When the info collecting process is done the Save icon will be enabled to ganerate the ebook.zip format and save to DB
